<p>The Hugo Award Administrators have asked us to not say anything until they are ready to issue a statement, and we are respecting their request. That is why at this time we are not adjusting the lists of finalists or taking any further action. The decisions about the Hugo Awards shortlist are in the hands of the current Hugo Award Administrators, not The Hugo Awards website.</p>
